<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
  <p>Hello <%= @invited_user.username %>,</p>

  <p><strong><%= @inviting_user.username %></strong> has invited you to join a Bible reading plan:</p>

  <div style="margin: 20px 0; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px;">
    <h2><%= @plan.name %></h2>
    <p><strong>Starting Date:</strong> <%= @plan_instance.start_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
    <p><strong>Duration:</strong> <%= @plan.days.size %> days</p>
  </div>

  <p>Click the button below to join this reading plan:</p>

  <p>
    <a href="<%= @confirmation_url %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">
      Join Reading Plan
    </a>
  </p>

  <p>If you didn't expect this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

  <p>Thank you,<br>
  AI Bible Plan Team</p>
</body>
</html>
